            "id": 6343662,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 陶氏(DOW-US)大跌5.01%，報32.3美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>陶氏(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DOW-US</a>)截至台北時間13日01:53股價下跌1.71美元，報32.30美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量7,461,695（股），盤中最高價34.43美元、最低價32.29美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.32%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.65%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.93%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>陶氏(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DOW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.7%</li> <li>近 1 月：+27.61%</li> <li>近 3 月：+50.61%</li> <li>近 6 月：+61%</li> <li>今年以來：+43.71%</li></ul></section></main>",
